                {/* Players, Hollow Gate, and Moderation are full-admin only
                    (Admin 1). Admin 2 (content role) gets the curation tabs:
                    Jutsus+Bloodlines, Events, VNs, AI Creator, Pet/Card
                    Editors, Village Leaders, Professions. */}
